nt. As was expected, it was found\nthat both molecular motions determined the glass dynamics at the same glass\ntransition temperature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 16 Apr 2023 21:59:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-18"}
