en the two tasks. Then, we propose a feature distillation (FD) loss that\nprovides extra structural regularization to help the HR depth estimation task\nlearn more scene structural knowledge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Apr 2023 03:24:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-18"}
