rs with the same stellar parameters selected from\nPS1. And the uncertainty becomes 0.31mag in i band for SSF-dM when comparing\nwith the stars with the same stellar parameters selected from APASS.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Apr 2023 09:04:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-10"}
