ch agents are built and trained. The proposed method is tested in the\nIEEE 39-bus system and a practical 710-bus regional power grid. Test results\nshow that the training process converges rapidly, the success rate of dispatch\nin both cases exceeds 99.70 percent, and the decision-making costs very little\ntime, which verifies the effectiveness and efficiency of the proposed method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Apr 2023 14:40:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-18"}
